---
title: Chicken, Mushroom & Onion Flatbreads  with Zucchini, Arugula Salad & Tomato
description: We love a classic pizza night, but tonight we’ll have to ask the tomato sauce to step aside—there’s a new kid in town. You’ll slather crispy flatbreads with a rich, savory Vidalia onion cream sauce we just can’t get enough of. Add tender, golden brown zucchini and earthy mushrooms, top it with a lemon-kissed arugula salad for bright contrast, and that’s it. Simple, satisfying, and all in 25 minutes—a hearty vegetarian dinner idea you just can’t pass up!
